A drug-sniffing dog had signalled that officers should look into the bag of the psychologist and, sure enough, they found quite a bit of heroine. After the truck driver's bag was flagged and searched, though, they were let go as it was apparently just a false alarm.

After the truck driver's bag was flagged and searched, though, they were let go as it was apparently just a false alarm.
